Program: Discovery
Title: Savant Syndrome
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxlv
Last Broadcast Date: 23 February 2000
Report on Savant Syndrome and the extraordinary mental abilities that savants tend to have. A programme about a form of autism which is accompanied by the ability to resolve complex mathematical problems, and in other cases a photographic memory with extreme attention to detail.